KPM REST API Specification
Version: v1
Architecture: RESTful API
Authentication: Supabase JWT Authentication
Content Type
application/json
Base URL
/api/v1

Authentication
Every request except login/signup requires
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>

Response Format
Success
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Feature created successfully.",
    "data": {}
}

Failure
{
    "success": false,
    "message": "Validation failed.",
    "errors": {}
}

